            <p>During my 6-month exchange at Saint Petersburg State University, I immersed myself in Russian culture while studying subjects such as business ethics, HR and international HR, financial analyses, knowledge management, and operations management. I also dedicated time to learning the Russian language, expanding my linguistic and cultural horizons. It was a transformative experience that broadened my knowledge and understanding of global business practices and fostered personal growth.</p>
